c: 3
v: 193
t: Wahe Po kamoe ka kamoe deunge Ureueng hei geuyue iman keu Allah Meuiman bandum akan Po gata Kamoe pih sigra iman le bagah Wahe Po kamoe Neuampon kamoe Dum dacha kamoe cit le sileupah Neuteuboh kamoe bak jeuheut kamoe ‘Oh mate kamoe beuroh meutuah Ngon ureueng nyang jroh Neupeuroh kamoe